			<h1 class="page-title">
				Monthly Archives: <span>June 2010</span>			</h1>




			<article id="post-102" class="post-102 post type-post hentry category-life">
			<header>
				<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902044319/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=102" title="Permalink to A Father’s Gift" rel="bookmark">A Father&#8217;s Gift</a></h2>
							</header>
				<div class="entry-summary">
				<p>The memory of my father is a puzzle I try to solve nearly every day, but today, of course, he is even more on my mind. Over and over, I lay out the pieces, the conversations and silences, over all &hellip; <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902044319/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=102">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
			</div><!-- .entry-summary -->
	
			<div class="entry-utility">
								<div class="entry-meta">
					<span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902044319/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?author=87" title="View all posts by LoriC">LoriC</a></span> <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902044319/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=102" title="10:09 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">June 20, 2010</span></a>				</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
													<span class="cat-links">
						<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902044319/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Life" rel="category">Life</a>					</span>
					<span class="meta-sep">|</span>
												<span class="comments-link"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902044319/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=102#comments" title="Comment on A Father’s Gift">3 Comments</a></span>
			</div><!-- .entry-utility -->
		</article><!-- #post-## -->

		
	

			<article id="post-101" class="post-101 post type-post hentry category-5">
			<header>
				<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902044319/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=101" title="Permalink to Spinning Out" rel="bookmark">Spinning Out</a></h2>
							</header>
				<div class="entry-summary">
				<p>Working on a novel, or story, or whatever it is, and fear I don&#8217;t have any extra juice for this blog. In fact, it&#8217;s probably better to get away from it and write something else. I&#8217;m in a good groove &hellip; <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902044319/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=101">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
			</div><!-- .entry-summary -->
	
			<div class="entry-utility">
								<div class="entry-meta">
					<span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902044319/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?author=87" title="View all posts by LoriC">LoriC</a></span> <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902044319/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=101" title="5:18 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">June 5, 2010</span></a>				</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
													<span class="cat-links">
						<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902044319/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in 5" rel="category">5</a>					</span>
					<span class="meta-sep">|</span>
												<span class="comments-link"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902044319/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=101#comments" title="Comment on Spinning Out">8 Comments</a></span>
			</div><!-- .entry-utility -->
		</article><!-- #post-## -->

		
	

